\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-field-group elementor-column elementor-field-type-submit elementor-col-100 e-form__buttons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<button class=\"elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" type=\"submit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Send<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/button>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/form>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-a4a4c7a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"a4a4c7a\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9098301\" data-id=\"9098301\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f372458 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f372458\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-large\">Habitat<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fa670f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fa670f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Oriental cockroaches, also known as water bugs or black beetles, are common household pests that thrive in warm and humid environments. These insects prefer to live in dark and damp areas such as basements, crawl spaces, and drains. They are usually found near water sources like leaky pipes or standing water.<\/p><p>One of the main reasons why Oriental cockroaches are attracted to humid habitats is because they need moisture to survive. In fact, these pests can only last for a few weeks without access to water. The humidity also helps them regulate their body temperature, which allows them to thrive in warmer climates.<\/p><p>If you suspect you have an infestation of Oriental cockroaches in your home, it\u2019s important to address the humidity levels and treat the problem with pesticides. This can include fixing any leaks or sources of moisture around your home and using dehumidifiers if necessary. By removing their preferred habitat conditions, you can help prevent future infestations from occurring.<\/p><p>Protect your home against the diverse threat of Oriental,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/wood-cockroaches\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><u><b>Wood\u00a0cockroaches<\/b><\/u><\/a><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">,\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/american-cockroaches\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b><u>American\u00a0cockroaches<\/u><\/b><\/a><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">, and\u00a0<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/smoky-brown-cockroaches\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b><u>Smoky Brown cockroaches<\/u><\/b><\/a><span style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">\u00a0with our comprehensive pest control guide to ensure a pest-free and comfortable environment.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7fad8ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7fad8ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-large\">Oriental Cockroaches Behavior<br><\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a605b04 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a605b04\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Oriental cockroaches are known for their aggressive and territorial behavior. They have a reputation for being one of the most influential and challenging pests to control. These cockroaches live in dark, damp spaces like basements, sewers, and drains. They can also be found in garbage dumps or around decaying organic matter.<\/p><p>These roaches are known to be aggressive towards each other when competing for resources, such as food or shelter. In addition to being territorial towards other roaches, they may also exhibit aggression towards humans who attempt to disturb them or threaten their space. Their bites can cause skin irritation and allergic reactions in some people.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8f96e3e elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8f96e3e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ccb1c33\" data-id=\"ccb1c33\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a1a7c3c\" data-id=\"a1a7c3c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b9cf51a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b9cf51a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Residential Pest Control Service<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-49a80ca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"49a80ca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Customized pest control treatments can be used to safeguard your living space against bothersome pests and ensure that they don&#8217;t become a nuisance in your home.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-45d85b6 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-global elementor-global-4670 elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"45d85b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-lg\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/appointment\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Book An Appointment<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-34ed4e7\" data-id=\"34ed4e7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3a24d21 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3a24d21\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-bb3ebd0\" data-id=\"bb3ebd0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-09bf231 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"09bf231\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-large\">Ways to control Oriental cockroaches<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33344f0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33344f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Keep your home clean and dry<\/strong>: Oriental cockroaches are attracted to damp, dark environments. This means that you should ensure that all spills are wiped up immediately, leaks in pipes are fixed promptly, and any areas of standing water (such as in sinks or bathtubs) are dried out as soon as possible.<\/p><p><strong>Seal up cracks and crevices:<\/strong> These cockroaches can fit through tiny spaces, so it\u2019s important to seal up any gaps or cracks in walls, floors, baseboards, and cabinets with caulk or weather stripping.<\/p><p><strong>Use insecticide:<\/strong> There are a variety of insecticides on the market that can be effective at killing Oriental cockroaches. Be sure to follow the instructions carefully when using these products and keep them away from pets and children.<\/p><p><strong>Set traps:<\/strong> Sticky traps or baited traps can be used to capture Oriental cockroaches. Place them in areas where you have seen evidence of these pests.<\/p><p><strong>Hire a professional pest control company:<\/strong> If your infestation is severe, it may be best to call ACME Pest Solutions with specialized knowledge of dealing with Oriental cockroach infestations safely and effectively.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4ea8251 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4ea8251\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c746034\" data-id=\"c746034\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57008d9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"57008d9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"Article\",\r